For those of you who may not know about it, there is extensive  
Cantera documentation here:

http://blue.caltech.edu/~dgg/html

In addition, I have just now set up an HTML documentation server for  
the Cantera python package. It is here:

http://blue.caltech.edu:1234/Cantera.html

And of course there is the Cantera wiki, although it is not used much:

http://www.cantera.org/wiki
